text: Louky van Olphen-van Amstel (born 14 April 1934) is a Dutch equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haarlem
